						 <p>A few of the sentences are oddly phrased, especially in the Description. This also doesn't have the impact that it's trying to go for, since there's very little to indicate that this person has an interest in people looking at her until she steals the guy's eyes.</p> <p>But besides that&#8230; eh. I liked the poem.</p> <p>+1.</p> 
