					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I didn’t know what I was expecting when I first read this, but it was surprisingly creepy! While it’s not the “monster” kind of scary, I still feel chills going up my spine, haha.</p> <p>There <em>is</em> one thing I was curious about, though. When all of Neigiecie disappeared except for his eyes, was that an example of 5303 “hijacking” his sight, or was that something else entirely?</p> 
				 	]]>
