						 <blockquote> <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><tt><strong><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IqFBdBWK9bc">Oh, knowing what we know, knowing what we don't know</a></strong></tt><br /> <tt><strong><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IqFBdBWK9bc">This is gonna change our world</a></strong></tt><br /> <tt><strong><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IqFBdBWK9bc">Feeling how I feel, I'll accept the unreal</a></strong></tt><br /> <tt><strong><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IqFBdBWK9bc">IF YOU BE MY NO EYED GIRL...</a></strong></tt></p> </div> <p style="text-align: center;"><sub><em>No Eyed Girl · Lemon Demon</em></sub></p> </blockquote> <p>It was either this or Touch-Tone Telephone this time around. I'll get to Touch-Tone later I guess. I don't like this one all that much, and may take it down or something if it doesn't get downvoted to hell.</p> <p><strong>Critique Peeps:</strong></p> <ul> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/deadly-bread" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3988532&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584244317" alt="Deadly Bread" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3988532)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/deadly-bread" >Deadly Bread</a></span> &#8212; <a class="newpage" href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-444-j">SCP-444-J</a></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3075960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1584244317" alt="stormbreath" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3075960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" >stormbreath</a></span> &#8212; <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5477">SCP-5477</a></li> <li>Scottyhoff</li> <li>WhoYouCallinAPinHead</li> </ul> <p><strong>Image Source:</strong></p> <ul> <li><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Wooded_grove.jpg">noeyed.jpg</a> &#8212; CC BY-SA 4.0, I know 4.0 is kinda iffy licensing-wise, but the image isn't that crucial to the article and any future translators can remove it from translations if needed.</li> </ul> <p style="text-align: center;"><sub><strong>&#171; <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5302">SWEET BOD</a> || SPIRIT PHONE SHUFFLE: NO EYED GIRL || <em>Don't hang up yet, I'm not done&#8230;</em> &#187;</strong></sub></p> 
